  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Save Zimbabwe&apos;s Chizarira National Park</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Chizarira National Park is one of Zimbabwe&apos;s last-remaining great wildernesses, but it has suffered a series of blows from fires, poaching and the destruction of almost all their infrastructure. A handful of determined rangers stay to defend the park&apos;s wildlife in extremely challenging conditions. ALERT has joined forces with Park Management to restore the park and revive its populations of iconic wildlife, including lion, elephant, leopard and the rare Taita falcon for the long term.</narrative>
  </description>
